John Milford https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Milford 0 John Milford (September 7, 1929 - August 14, 2000) was an American actor in theatre, television, and films, playing scores of roles, often as a western villain. He was estimated to have had about 500 appearances in TV roles.
